{"tid":2189821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"揭露拜登家族與支共黑暗交易《騎龍：拜登的中國秘密》","createTime":"2020-09-05T07:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T10:37:34.000Z","uid":294518,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"20b0f7fd819a19f13811f93ba942cd0e6d7b5849","tid":2189821,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:09:27.000Z","msg":"今天支共對美國的又一黑暗交易被美媒徹底曝光！<br />\n<br />\n即使不是有史以來金額最高的藍金黃，個人感覺應該會是最有名的藍金黃了！<br />\n亨特&middot;拜登（Hunter Biden），美國前副總統喬&middot;拜登的次子， 於2013年12月其父作為美國副總統訪華期間一同前往北京，作為一個毫無金融背景、沒有中國人脈、因吸食可卡因而被美國海軍開除的官2代，在那次北京之行後，他投資的咨詢公司立即收到了一筆來自中共的高達10億美金的投資。至此以後，他投資或合作的公司，從美國買到很多敏感的、根本不可能出口到中共的技術，被賣到了中共軍方，比如說賣給中國航空工業總公司 (AVIC, Aviation Industry Corporation of China) 的一些戰鬥機和無人機的技術、通過渤海華美（Bohai Harvest）賣給中共軍方的人臉識別技術、投資的中廣核（CGN， China General Nuclear），一個被FBI調查的公司，後被證實其中一個工程師自1998開始就從美國偷竊機密核資料。<br />\n<br />\n另外，此紀錄片中還提及了<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">何志平 </span></span>（Patrick Ho Chi-ping ， 他的太太就是大名鼎鼎的演員胡慧中。作為香港首位眼外科教授，何志平曾任全國政協委員）。何志平於2017年在美國被捕，罪名是他代表一家中國（和中共軍方有關係的）能源集團在美國行賄。 他在被FBI美國聯邦調查局拘捕調查期間，就打過2個電話，其中一個就是打給喬&middot;拜登的哥哥，詹姆斯&middot;拜登。 當然，片子還提及了2014年的烏克蘭醜聞、喬&middot;拜登姐姐的咨詢公司、以及美國前總統奧巴馬。水當真很深啊！<br />\n<br />\n有興趣的朋友可以去觀看長達45分鐘的完整紀錄片《騎龍：拜登的中國秘密》。鏈接如下：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=JRmlcEBAiIs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dyoutu.be%26v%3DJRmlcEBAiIs&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs44leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=08ff15cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=youtu.be&amp;v=JRmlcEBAiIs</a> [/u]"},{"pid":"ebccf14dc1a3e9dc7738bff3cd7032ef4d140535","tid":2189821,"uid":43204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc70425a4b3cebaa0fb8fd9ca706c9602efc1fa0","tid":2189821,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:20:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ddcc3dbcf6bcfbc1860ab3d0d6a49270ce1e1ff","tid":2189821,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:21:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">騎龍？<br />\n<br />\n龍騎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1cf4089784c7a1b03aa7a4a784cd67f57db6fe73","tid":2189821,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fd003bc2beb2df34409d877d8616fb9880cde9","tid":2189821,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWY6XEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWY6XEQ.jpg&h=6d22b5ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZC6016x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZC6016x.jpg&h=d6145a38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adfcdbca3eb98c74a72cc0f89e1a1b1c5842bed2","tid":2189821,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2724cc5d5a1acfb3d26f18b338f42b7742132b52","tid":2189821,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98800f53cac289af2ead632fc1f2b2f3a13d1d5e","tid":2189821